1</span><br><span class=\"line\">VAR end_conditions = 0</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">+ [开始游戏] -&gt; start</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">== start</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">璃落放学后回到了家中，发现家里的大门竟然开着……</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">+ “姐姐又忘记锁门了……” -&gt; not_vigilant1</span><br><span class=\"line\">+ “难道家里进小偷了？” -&gt; vigilant1</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">== vigilant1</span><br><span class=\"line\">~ vigilant = 1</span><br><span class=\"line\">-&gt; drawing_room</span><br><span class=\"line\">== not_vigilant1</span><br><span class=\"line\">~ vigilant = -1</span><br><span class=\"line\">-&gt; drawing_room</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">== drawing_room</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">璃落来到了客厅。</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;vigilant &gt; 0:</span><br><span class=\"line\">+ [打电话报警] -&gt; end1</span><br><span class=\"line\">+ [打开收音机] -&gt; radio</span><br><span class=\"line\">+ [走向其他房间] -&gt; other_room</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#123;vigilant &lt; 0:</span><br><span class=\"line\">+ [坐上沙发] -&gt; sofa</span><br><span class=\"line\">+ [打开收音机] -&gt; radio</span><br><span class=\"line\">+ [走向其他房间] -&gt; other_room</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">== sofa</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">璃落坐在沙发上。</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">+ [有点困了] -&gt; sleepy</span><br><span class=\"line\">+ [有点无聊] -&gt; boring</span><br><span class=\"line\">+ [回退] -&gt; drawing_room</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">= sleepy</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">~ end_conditions = sleepy